# 🌭 Hot Dog Toppings Suggester

An interactive web app that suggests unique hot dog toppings based on users' favorite foods and drinks using the **Google Gemini API**.

---

## 🚀 Features
- **Interactive Quiz**: Users input their favorite foods and drinks.
- **AI-Powered Suggestions**: Uses Google Gemini API to generate creative hot dog toppings.
- **Backend Security**: API requests are handled securely via an Express.js backend.
- **Simple & Responsive UI**: Clean frontend interface built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

---

